'''Wagner Fabrício Cardoso de Pina''' ({{IPA|pt|ˈvag.nɛɾ fɐ.ˈbɾi.si.u kɐɾ.ˈdo.zu dɨ ˈpi.nɐ|lang}}; born 3 November 2002) is a professional footballer who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Süper Lig]] club [[Trabzonspor]]. Born in Portugal, he plays for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Wagner Pina|website=Soccerway|accessdate=30 May 2024|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/wagner-fabricio-cardoso-pina/770880/}}</ref>

==Club career==
In 2021, Pina started his professional career with CD Gouveia in the [[Campeonato de Portugal (league)|Campeonato de Portugal]] and the following year he moved to [[C.F. Os Belenenses|Belenenses]] in [[Liga 3 (Portugal)|Liga 3]], joining in July 2022.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.osbelenenses.com/2022/07/wagner-pina-chega-do-gouveia-com-grande-margem-de-progressao/|website=osbeleneses|accessdate=30 May 2024|title= Wagner Pina arrives from Gouveia with a large margin of progression|date=7 June 2022}}</ref> The following season he joined Estoril and predominantly played initially with their U23 side, but made his senior debut in the [[Taça da Liga]] in a victory against [[FC Paços de Ferreira|Paços de Ferreira]] in July 2023.<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.abola.pt/futebol/noticias/estoril-wagner-pina-soma-minutos-na-taca-e-e-alternativa-para-a-direita-2023102316233649768 |website=abola.pt|accessdate=30 May 2024|title= Estoril: Wagner Pina adds minutes in the Cup and is an alternative to the right|date=23 October 2023}}</ref> He made his debut in the [[Primeira Liga]] on 28 October 2023 against [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]] and began playing regularly at right-back from the team that autumn.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-betclic/estoril/detalhe/lateral-wagner-pina-ganha-espaco|date=5 November 2023|title=Full-back Wagner Pina gains space at Estoril|website=Record.pt|accessdate=30 May 2024}}</ref> On 24 November 2023, he renewed his contract until 2027.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvi.iol.pt/noticias/estoril/liga/estoril-renova-com-wagner-pina|website=tvi.oil.pt|access-date=30 May 2024|title= Estoril renova com Wagner Pina|date=24 November 2024}}</ref>

On 21 June 2025, [[Süper Lig]] club Trabzonspor announced the signing of Pina on a four-year contract, for a fee of €3 million.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.larende.com/haber/wagner-pina-trabzonsporda-106638.html|title=Wagner Pina, Trabzonspor'da
|publisher=larende.com |access-date=21 June 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
Pina made his debut for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] on 21 March 2024, in a 1–0 win against [[Guyana national football team|Guyana]].<ref>{{cite web|url= https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2024/03/21/world/friendlies/cape-verde-islands/guyana/4327963/|website=Soccerway|accessdate=30 May 2024|date=21 March 2024|title= CABO VERDE VS. GUYANA 1 - 0}}</ref> In May 2024, he was called-up for his first competitive fixtures in 2026 World Cup Qualifying matches against Cameroon and Libya.

